com.jibrok.jira.plugins.messagefield.config.dto

Class FormIssue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jibrok.jira.plugins.messagefield.config.dto.FormIssue

  • public class FormIssue
extends java.lang.Object
    Object contains data from form (raw text from json form serialization) and issue. In this object, all raw data is validated and converted to java objects. If the validation of the field value was successful, the value will be set to null.
